Besides, we'll only need to invite those closest to us as guests.

23
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:23,399
 If this isn't a dream wedding, then what will be? 

24
00:02:23,399 --> 00:02:27,000
I'm so considerate that even Sister Ling would be driven to tears.

25
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,600
 Jingjing, roll call! 

26
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:30,159
Coming!

27
00:02:30,159 --> 00:02:33,879
That's it for now. Hurry and sign up. I have a filming session.

28
00:02:33,879 --> 00:02:38,099
Okay. I'll go check it out. Good luck with your shoot.

29
00:02:39,720 --> 00:02:42,120
What was that about?

30
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,679
Our wedding.

31
00:02:43,679 --> 00:02:45,558
What's it going to be?

32
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:47,680
I've never been to a celebrity wedding.

33
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:50,819
Is it going to be grandiose? Do I need to wear a suit?

34
00:02:50,819 --> 00:02:54,739
She told me to reserve a spot at the group wedding organized by our unit.

35
00:02:54,739 --> 00:02:56,340
What?

36
00:02:58,120 --> 00:03:02,860
Your girlfriend is a celebrity, and that's what she could come up with?

37
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:05,219
But then again, it really suits you.

38
00:03:05,219 --> 00:03:09,519
Didn't you say to keep it simple when you took part in our colleague's wedding?

39
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:13,560
When did I say that?

40
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,260
Years ago.

41
00:03:17,599 --> 00:03:20,400
Well? Are you going to sign up?

42
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,998
No way.

43
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,817
She'll change her mind in a few days.

44
00:03:24,817 --> 00:03:28,439
After all, Ms Qiao's plan took us from the beach to the grass,

45
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:32,659
to the hotel, and to the beach again.

46
00:03:52,080 --> 00:03:54,880
 Are you off-duty? Have you signed up? 

47
00:04:03,890 --> 00:04:07,360
- Are you serious? 
 - Of course. You haven't signed up yet, have you?

48
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:10,637
There are only twelve spots. Hurry and sign up.

49
00:04:10,639 --> 00:04:12,319
You can't change your mind after you sign up.

50
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:14,390
Otherwise, you'll waste spots for others.

51
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:16,480
Are you sure that you won't change your mind?

52
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,040
Of course not.

53
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,639
I was a little impulsive that day.

54
00:04:19,639 --> 00:04:21,839
But now the more I think about it, the more appropriate it is.

55
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,659
 Before we talk about appropriateness, 

56
00:04:23,659 --> 00:04:27,959
 have you even taken your parents and also Sister Ling into consideration? 

57
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,977
Will they agree?

58
00:04:29,977 --> 00:04:31,517
Never mind about Sister Ling.

59
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:35,160
As for Mom and Dad, I'll take care of it.

60
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:37,140
 If they agree, then you'll sign up? 

61
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:38,160
Yes.

62
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:40,115
I'll go ask them now.

63
