 - Yu Tu.  
 - Auntie, I was in the lab.

71
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,720
 Jingjing called us. 

72
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:23,000
 She said she wanted to join the group wedding organized by your unit. 

73
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,215
 Are you aware of this? 

74
00:05:26,519 --> 00:05:28,358
Yes, she told me.

75
00:05:29,399 --> 00:05:31,423
But I don't think it's appropriate.

76
00:05:37,079 --> 00:05:41,059
 I see. Jingjing made several calls to tell me this. 

77
00:05:41,059 --> 00:05:43,800
 At first, I firmly disapproved of it. 

78
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:47,059
 But somehow, she won me over. 

79
00:05:47,059 --> 00:05:49,839
Haven't you two come to an agreement?

80
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,079
I thought you wouldn't agree.

81
00:05:53,080 --> 00:05:57,160
We and Jingjing's parents sat down for a meal just to talk about this.

82
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:59,040
 And then, she won over her parents, too. 

83
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:01,098
 They were kind of pleased. 

84
00:06:02,639 --> 00:06:06,319
Son, if you have any reservations about this,

85
00:06:06,319 --> 00:06:08,839
you can talk it over with her.

86
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:10,579
Yes, Mom.

87
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,680
Yu Tu, aren't you joining us for dinner? We need to work overtime.

88
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,980
You guys go ahead. I'm going home.

89
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:38,959
That workaholic is ditching overtime today.

90
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:43,703
The big star is filming right now, isn't she? Why is he going home so early?

91
00:07:09,158 --> 00:07:12,598
 Mr. Yu, you've been through a really rough day. 

92
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:14,757
 Life needs a sense of ritual. 

93
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:16,199
 I'm a pragmatist. 

94
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:18,760
 Well I'm here. Your pragmatism has to go. 

95
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:21,800
 See, isn't it much better? 

96
